## Project Structure

```
MustangMeals/
├── App.js                          # Navigation setup
├── app.json                        # Expo + store config
├── eas.json                        # EAS build + submit config
├── package.json                    # Dependencies + build scripts
├── assets/                         # Icon + splash screen (add these!)
│   ├── icon.png
│   ├── splash.png
│   └── adaptive-icon.png
└── src/
    ├── data/
    │   └── spots.js                # Campus food spots + reviews
    ├── screens/
    │   ├── HomeScreen.js           # Browse & search
    │   ├── DetailScreen.js         # Spot info + reviews
    │   └── WriteReviewScreen.js    # Submit a review
    └── theme.js                    # Colors & typography
```

